 00:00, 08:00, and 16:00 UTC using a time-weighted average of the premium index. Funding payments occur between long and short position holders, with rates typically ranging from -0.5% to +0.5% during normal market conditions. The exchange uses a mark price mechanism that averages spot prices from multiple venues to prevent manipulation during funding calculations."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
